    helpText: 'Installing your first smart lights provides immediate tangible benefits while giving you hands-on experience with device setup, app management, and basic automation before expanding to more complex systems. Start with simple smart bulbs or switches in your most-used room to test connectivity, practice creating scenes and schedules, and experience daily automation benefits. This practical implementation builds confidence with your chosen ecosystem and reveals any setup challenges or usability issues that should be addressed before investing in additional smart home devices.'
