    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Smart door locks provide immediate security benefits and convenient keyless entry while serving as an excellent introduction to home automation implementation. Choose locks compatible with your automation ecosystem and install them on front door, back door, and garage entry to experience daily automation benefits like automatic locking at bedtime or unlocking when you arrive home. This foundational security upgrade gives you hands-on experience with device installation and integration while providing tangible safety and convenience improvements that demonstrate the value of home automation to your entire household.'
  }
];</parameter>
